{"tid":1927303,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】巴士司機確診","createTime":"2020-03-15T16:58:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-15T17:52:21.000Z","uid":249945,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"989ad42d90174ac05d9216c374858071058965d2","tid":1927303,"uid":249945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T16:58:02.000Z","msg":"【曾駕駛90 96 98號的巴士司機確診】<br />\n<br />\n我地收到記者朋友既通知，指有巴士司機確診武漢肺炎。該名司機於3月11日至13日曾駕駛90、96、98號巴士，如果呢三日坐過呢三架巴士的大家請注意，有任何不適要立即睇醫生。<br />\n<br />\n司機於三日內曾駕駛的巴士車牌：FN9505、9123、8181、9102、9132、8189、8439、8251。<br />\n<br />\n我地已經同城巴聯絡，要求佢地消毒、清潔以上巴士，如情況許可，希望隔離以上巴士一段時間。<br />\n<br />\n城巴回覆已知悉有司機確診，相關車輛會封車並全面消毒。"},{"pid":"0695aa3b5e646148a66b2ca425acc088a5fc1da6","tid":1927303,"uid":249945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T16:58:52.000Z","msg":"source<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10220063779679333&amp;id=1069623440\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D10220063779679333%26id%3D1069623440&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2BvhURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=fe28e6b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10220063779679333&amp;id=1069623440</a>"},{"pid":"7398f055efac5c99edb3cc741800f1e7c752531d","tid":1927303,"uid":249945,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T16:59:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8xzwXHO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8xzwXHO.jpg&h=0b96d8b4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bff3b8e9b454d8ba7aabef5314223821070d5900","tid":1927303,"uid":55162,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T16:59:58.000Z","msg":"都遇過唔少巴士司機冇戴口罩<br />\n特別係N車"},{"pid":"5dc598f98ee25b74ad13892b422e67e6337c8c6c","tid":1927303,"uid":249945,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T17:00:51.000Z","msg":"南區"},{"pid":"9cc9692e0b7a04c98cb4a8389e90eee64152867f","tid":1927